Class PushBlockStream

java.lang.Object
org.apache.spark.network.shuffle.protocol.BlockTransferMessage
org.apache.spark.network.shuffle.protocol.PushBlockStream
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.apache.spark.network.protocol.Encodable
public class PushBlockStream extends BlockTransferMessage
Request to push a block to a remote shuffle service to be merged in push based shuffle. The remote shuffle service will also include this message when responding the push requests.
Since:
3.1.0
